title: Coronavirus update: Chinese death count revised but Government denies cover-up, UK develops vaccine taskforce
description: The Chinese Government denies allegations it intentionally dragged its feet in reporting the true death toll in Wuhan, the UK develops a taskforce to speed up the development of a vaccine, and Dubai's strict lockdown carries on another week.
content:
Posted 
April 18, 2020 05:28:24
Allegations the Chinese Government intentionally covered up the official death toll in Wuhan have been denied by Beijing.
